Reason has poured his heart out about the pain he feels after HHP's death earlier this week. Reason described HHP as his "big brother" and reflected on a trip they took together in 2015. "It was like going on a road trip with my big brother for the first time in forever," he said. Reason said Jabba was an open book who gave an abundance of love. "He definitely had his fair share of controversies and mistakes but my ni**a gave love. Real, pure, uncut, honest and genuine love always. Even when he needed it, he always chose to give it," Reason added. Here's the full post: